							<h3><a href="#">About PVKK Institute Of Technology</a></h3>
						<p >PVKK Institute of Technology is one of the best Engineering Institutions, established in the year 2008 by Sri Balaji Education Society under the aegis and the vision of Dr. Palle Raghunatha Reddy Garu with a holistic objective to promote quality technical education in Anantapur city. The institution is affiliated to JNTU Anantapur and is approved by AICTE, New Delhi.</p>
						<p >PVKKIT has made its beginning on a humble note with 240 student intake with 4 UG courses. Since its inception, it has been actively nurturing and catering to the academic needs of young technocrats moulding them into good engineers and is making rapid strides to reach the pinnacle of success. Presently, the institution, with an intake of 480 seats, offers 5 UG (B.Tech. - CSE, ECE, EEE, ME, & CE) and 5 PG courses (M.Tech. – CSE, ECE, EEE, ME, & CE) along with MBA and II shift Diploma Courses. </p>
						<p >The college is housed in a serene atmosphere, spreading in 26 acres amidst lush green land, making it an ideal place of learning. The state-of-the-art infrastructure, with well-ventilated and furnished classrooms, well-equipped laboratories, ample amount of space for the workshops, technology-enhanced digital classrooms and drawing halls, are but few of the quality amenities provided by the institution. Sports and Games are given much priority and college is having plenty of open space to conduct a variety of outdoor games. The central library of the college is the hub of knowledge, stocked with more than 40,000+ books and volumes, access to the digital libraries, and subscriptions to renowned journals, help students in acquiring more information. The college canteen serves quality and hygiene food at a subsidized price. The college provides hostel facilities for boys and girls separately and accommodates 400 boys and 300 girl students.</p>
						<p >The qualified, experienced, research-oriented and dedicated team of faculty members are the core strength of the institution. They work in unison with the mission and vision of the college and provide their expertise in an amicable way to the student community. Their frequent rapport with the industry gives them an edge in understanding the needs of the industry.<br />
<br />To further academic excellence among students, we have Student Chapters for each branch of engineering. They conduct seminars and quizzes on technical topics and organize technical and industrial visits. They also provide exposure to the students on current technologies by arranging lectures of eminent persons from Academia and industry. 
</p>
                        <p>To enhance academic excellence, student chapters are initiated separately for each department to provide students with: </p>
                            <ol>
								<li>Hands-on experience by participating in workshops</li>
								 <li>Exposure through the interaction (guest lectures, seminars) with industry experts and reputed academicians</li>
								 <li>Participation in co-curricular activities (Seminars, Quizzes)</li>
								 <li>Industrial visits</li>
							</ol>
                        <p>With the quality of education and the standard facilities, the institution stands as one of the top engineering colleges and is incessantly trying to offer the best.</p> 

